@startuml
title SEDCM MVP - Diagrama de Arquitectura

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam wrapWidth 220

actor "Operador" as operador

node "Docker Compose" {
  package "Simuladores" {
    [cAdvisor Bridge\n(simulators/cadvisor-bridge)] as cadvisor
    [Environment Simulator\n(simulators/environment)] as envsim
  }

  queue "Mosquitto\nMQTT Broker" as mqtt

  component "Backend\nFastAPI + Rules Engine\n(backend/app)" as backend
  database "PostgreSQL\ntelemetry_samples\nrack_state\naudit_log\nprocessed_message" as postgres

  component "Edge Executor\nDocker Adapter + Idempotency\n(edge-executor/app)" as edge
  component "Dashboard\nHTTP + WebSocket\n(dashboard/src)" as dashboard
}

cloud "Docker API Local" as dockerapi

operador --> dashboard : Consulta estado\ny eventos en tiempo real

cadvisor --> mqtt : publica telemetría\ndc/telemetria/zona/{Z}/rack/{R}/host/{H}/contenedor/{C}
envsim --> mqtt : publica variables\nambientales (temp/hum/power)

mqtt --> backend : consume telemetría
backend -> backend : fusión cAdvisor + ambiental\nvalidación + reglas + histéresis
backend --> postgres : persiste telemetría/estado/auditoría

backend --> mqtt : publica comando\ndc/comandos/zona/{Z}/rack/{R}\naction=stop_critico
mqtt --> edge : consume comando\n(idempotencia command_id)

edge --> dockerapi : stop contenedor crítico\nlabels dc.zone/dc.rack/dc.critical=true
edge --> mqtt : publica ACK\ndc/eventos/zona/{Z}/rack/{R} status=ok|fail

mqtt --> backend : consume ACK/eventos
backend --> postgres : guarda ACK y trazabilidad

backend --> dashboard : REST (snapshot)
backend --> dashboard : WebSocket (eventos y cambios de estado)

note right of backend
  Principios implementados:
  - Seguridad térmica primero
  - Desacoplamiento por MQTT
  - Trazabilidad y auditoría
  - Idempotencia
  - Histéresis anti-flapping
end note

@enduml
